## Why This Is Asked
This question tests system design expertise, scalability knowledge, and production experience with high-traffic scenarios—critical skills for enterprise clients handling massive concurrent user loads.

## Expected Answer
Candidates should discuss: DNS-level load balancing with geographic distribution, L7 vs L4 load balancers, health checking strategies, circuit breaker patterns, auto-scaling policies, database sharding, multi-tier caching layers, comprehensive monitoring, and failover scenarios. Must address capacity planning and zero-downtime deployment strategies.

## Code Example
